data.description: This adorable two bedroom 1 bath home is situated on huge corner lot and has so much potential!  The main level offers large kitchen, nice sized living room with wood floors, 2 bedrooms, main floor laundry & full bath.  The basement has tons of storage and great finished family room space perfect for entertaining!  The roof was just replaced in Nov 2023!  This is a must see!
